---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <main class="pt-28 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-16">
        <p class="font-body text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-teal mb-4">Our Story</p>
        <h1 class="font-display text-6xl text-navy mb-6">About Sage & Serum</h1>
        <p class="font-body text-base text-navy/60 leading-relaxed">
          Sage & Serum was inspired by the belief that skin health and wellness should be accessible to everybody. Rooted in clean, sustainable, results oriented, certified skincare and tailored to each individual, Sage & Serum is an inclusive skin care studio curated to genuinely care for you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Two col: image + bio -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start mb-16">
        <div class="aspect-[3/4] rounded-3xl bg-blush/40 overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src="https://placehold.co/600x800/E4DBD2/2D4A52?text=Dawn"
            alt="Dawn Kratofil"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl text-navy">Hi, I'm <em>Dawn</em></h2>
          <p class="font-body text-sm text-navy/60 leading-relaxed">
            Born and raised in Southern California, I grew up in a small community within the Ventura County Line that nestles against the base of the Santa Monica mountains. Every evening the coastal fog would roll in over Boney Mountain Peak to create the most serene backdrop. I often look back on growing up in this very special surf community with great appreciation and awe.
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-sm text-navy/60 leading-relaxed">
            After 25 years of living in the hills of my beloved Northeast Los Angeles (NELA), and working one on one coaching clients to make therapeutic lifestyle change, I felt the California coast I love so much call me back. In 2022, I decided to take my years of professional experience and blend it with my lifelong interest in skin care, and became a licensed esthetician. 2024 brought me to South Orange County and back to the coastal influence and surf community I had been longing to reconnect with.
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-sm text-navy/60 leading-relaxed">
            I have always felt very passionate about making a positive difference in the lives of others and am pleased my skin care practice allows me to carry this deeply held intention forward.
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-sm text-navy/60 leading-relaxed">
            Outside of work, my husband and I enjoy spending time with our two kitties, traveling the world, cooking healthy meals, snow skiing, hiking and paddle boarding. For me, connecting to nature brings a great sense of peace, so I strive to spend time outdoors everyday. On weekends, you will often find me dancing barefoot around the house listening to my vinyl record collection.
          </p>
          <div class="pt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            {['Licensed Esthetician', 'EcoCert Trained', 'Functional Medicine Health Coach'].map(tag => (
              <span class="font-body text-xs text-teal border border-teal/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5">
                {tag}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
          <div class="pt-2 border-t border-silver">
            <p class="font-body text-sm text-navy font-medium mt-4">Dawn Kratofil</p>
            <p class="font-body text-xs text-navy/50">Founder & Licensed Esthetician</p>
            <a href="mailto:dawn@sageandserumskin.com" class="font-body text-xs text-teal hover:text-navy transition-colors">
              dawn@sageandserumskin.com
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>